    public class GuestbookImpl
extends GuestbookBaseImpl
    The extended model implementation for the Guestbook service. Represents a row in the "GB_Guestbook" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    Helper methods and all application logic should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the Guestbook interface.
